<paragraph blockId="34.[94,1301,2462,3167]" box="[97,469,2902,2931]" pageId="34" pageNumber="633">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[97,231,2902,2931]" pageId="34" pageNumber="633">Breeding.</emphasis>
No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="34" pageNumber="633" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="34.[94,1301,2462,3167]" pageId="34" pageNumber="633">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[95,331,2934,2968]" pageId="34" pageNumber="633">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Mauritanian Gerbils are probably nocturnal and terrestrial, digging burrows.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
