</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="34" pageNumber="633" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="34.[94,1301,2462,3167]" pageId="34" pageNumber="633">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[97,449,3056,3085]" pageId="34" pageNumber="633">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List, where it is considered a synonym of 
<taxonomicName box="[275,434,3092,3126]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Gerbillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="34" pageNumber="633" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="nancillus">G. nancillus</taxonomicName>
. Recent expeditionsin region of type locality failed to catch new specimens of the Mauritanian Gerbil.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
